ge F.C.|Liversedge]]||[[Hall Road Rangers]]\n|-\n|2008\u201309||[[Nostell Miners Welfare F.C.|Nostell]]||[[Staveley Miners Welfare F.C.|Staveley Miners Welfare]]\n|-\n|2009\u201310||[[Winterton Rangers F.C.|Winterton Rangers]]||[[Staveley Miners Welfare F.C.|Staveley Miners Welfare]]\n|-\n|2010\u201311||[[Tadcaster Albion F.C.|Tadcaster Albion]]||[[Glasshoughton Welfare F.C.|Glasshoughton Welfare]]\n|-\n|2011\u201312||[[Handsworth F.C. (2003)|Handsworth]]||[[Grimsby Borough F.C.|Grimsby Borough]]\n|}\n\n==Member clubs in national competitions==\n===FA Cup First Round===\nThe following NCEL clubs have reached the First Round proper of the [[FA Cup]] \u2013\n{| class=wikitable\t\t\n!Season\t\t\t\n!NCEL Club\n!Round\n!Venue\n!Result\t\n!Opponents\n|-\n|[[1982\u201383 FA Cup|1982\u201383]]||[[Shepshed Charterhouse F.C.|Shepshed Charterhouse]]||1st||Away||Lost 1\u20135||[[Preston North End F.C.|Preston North End]]\n|-\n|[[1990\u201391 FA Cup|1990\u201301]]||[[Spennymoor United F.C.|Spennymoor United]]||1st||Away||Lost 2\u20133||[[Chesterfield F.C.|Chesterfield]]\n|-\n|[[2001\u201302 FA Cup|2001\u201302]]||[[Brigg Town F.C.|Brigg Town]]||1st||Away||Lost 1\u20134||[[Tranmere Rovers F.C.|Tranmere Rovers]]\n|-\n|[[2002\u201303 FA Cup|2002\u201303]]||[[Harrogate Railway Athletic F.C.|Harrogate Railway Athletic]]||1st<br>2nd||Away<br>Home||Won 2\u20131<br>Lost 1\u20133||[[Slough Town F.C.|Slough Town]]<br>[[Bristol City F.C.|Bristol City]]\n|}\n\n===FA Vase finalists===\nThe following NCEL clubs have reached the Final of the [[FA Vase]] \u2013\n{| class=wikitable\t\t\n!Season\t\t\t\n!NCEL Club\n!Result\t\n!Opponents\n|-\n|1987\u201388||[[Emley A.F.C. (1903)|Emley]]||Lost 0\u20131||[[Colne Dynamoes F.C.|Colne Dynamoes]]\n|-\n|1989\u201390||[[Bridlington Town F.C.|Bridlington Town]]||Lost 0\u20131||[[Yeading F.C.|Yeading]]\n|-\n|1990\u201391||[[Guiseley A.F.C.|Guiseley]]||'''Won''' 3\u20131||[[Gresley Rovers F.C.|Gresley Rovers]]\n|-\n|1995\u201396||[[Brigg Town F.C.|Brigg Town]