n===President's Cup and Trophy===\nIn the past the league has had additional cup competitions. The Trophy was contested by the Division One clubs and the President's Cup which featured the top eight teams in each division from the previous season, provided they remain in the league.\n\n====Winners====\n{| class=wikitable\t\t\n!Season\t\t\t\n!President's Cup\t\t\n!Trophy\t\t\t\n|-\n|1990\u201391||[[North Ferriby United F.C.|North Ferriby United]]\t\n|-\n|1991\u201392||[[North Shields F.C.|North Shields]]\t\n|-\n|1992\u201393||[[Maltby Main F.C.|Maltby Miners Welfare]]\t\n|-\n|1993\u201394||[[Lincoln United F.C.|Lincoln United]]\t\n|-\n|1994\u201395||[[Arnold Town F.C.|Arnold Town]]\t\n|-\n|1995\u201396||[[Belper Town F.C.|Belper Town]]||[[Pontefract Collieries]] \n|-\n|1996\u201397||[[Hucknall Town F.C.|Hucknall Town]]||[[Garforth Town]]\n|-\n|1997\u201398||[[Glasshoughton Welfare F.C.|Glasshoughton Welfare]]||[[Staveley Miners Welfare F.C.|Staveley Miners Welfare]]\n|-\n|1998\u201399||[[North Ferriby United F.C.|North Ferriby United]]||[[Yorkshire Amateur F.C.|Yorkshire Amateur]]\n|-\n|1999\u201300||[[North Ferriby United F.C.|North Ferriby United]]||[[Goole AFC|Goole]]\n|-\n|2000\u201301||[[Selby Town F.C.|Selby Town]]||[[Pickering Town]]\n|-\n|2001\u201302||[[Alfreton Town F.C.|Alfreton Town]]||[[Bridlington Town]]\n|-\n|2002\u201303||[[Harrogate Railway Athletic F.C.|Harrogate Railway Athletic]]||[[Mickleover Sports]]\n|-\n|2003\u201304||[[Eastwood Town F.C.|Eastwood Town]]||[[Hall Road Rangers]]\n|-\n|2004\u201305||[[Buxton F.C.|Buxton]]||[[Lincoln Moorlands F.C.|Lincoln Moorlands]]\n|-\n|2005\u201306||[[Buxton F.C.|Buxton]]||[[Retford United]]\n|-\n|2006\u201307||[[Retford United F.C.|Retford United]]||[[Parkgate F.C.|Parkgate]]\n|-\n|2007\u201308||[[Liversedge F.C.|Liversedge]]||[[Hall Road Rangers]]\n|-\n|2008\u201309||[[Nostell Miners Welfare F.C.|Nostell]]||[[Staveley Miners Welfare F.C.|Staveley Miners Welfare]]\n|-\n|2009\u201310||[[Winterton Rangers F.C.